title: Which Fantasy Quarterbacks Do You Want in 2019? l The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly and Danny Heifetz make their triumphant return in 2019 by declaring which fantasy football quarterback they trust with their life, which quarterback’s bandwagon is so full it’s destined to crash, and why Josh Allen is better than Baker Mayfield.

Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
